title: Lakers Tonight with Jason Timpf - Lebron and Russ pull out the win
itunes:title: Lakers Tonight with Jason Timpf - Lebron and Russ pull out the win
description:
Jason breaks down the Lakers gutsy win over the Raptors, Embiid and Luka's battle, and why Chicago will still be a tough out in the playoffs despite their loss to Phoenix.
